name: Wealthsimple Developed Markets ex North America Socially Responsible Index ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible. The fund invests primarily in equity securities of companies in Europe, Australasia and the Far East with the goal of achieving diversified exposure to companies that do not violate commonly held social and environmental values.
